<h1>Sign up</h1>

<form action="/insert_member" method="post">

  <div>
    <label for="username_box">Username</label>
    <input id="username_box" name="query_username" placeholder="Choose a username..." type="text">
  </div>
                 
  <div>
    <label for="first_name_box">First name</label>
      
    <input type="text" id="first_name_box" name="query_first_name">
  </div>
         
  <div>
    <label for="last_name_box">Last name</label>
      
    <input type="text" id="last_name_box" name="query_last_name">
  </div>
    
  <div>
    <label for="password_box">Password</label>
    <input id="password_box" name="query_password" placeholder="Choose a password..." type="password">
  </div>

  <div>
    <label for="password_confirmation_box">Password Confirmation</label>
    <input id="password_confirmation_box" name="query_password_confirmation" placeholder="Confirm your password..." type="password">
  </div>

  <button>
    Sign up
  </button>
</form>

<hr>

<p>
  Or, <a href="/member_sign_in">Sign in</a> instead.
</p>

<p>
  Wait, are you directly affected by Danish immigration rules? <a href="/user_sign_up">Click here!</a>
</p>

<p>If no, finish the workflow and only store in Members table</p>

<p>If yes, ask the following questions to input the Users table</p>

<ul>
  <li>1) What is your first and last name?</li>

  <li>2) What is your country of origin?</li>

  <li>3) Do you work in any of the following industries? Business, Environment, Health</li>

  <li>4) Which municipality do you reside in?</li>

  <li>5) In a couple of sentences, what is your personal story?</li>

  <li>6) Can you paste a link to a photo of yourself?</li>

  <li>7) Various permissions -> TRUE / FALSE</li> 
